168
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:26,980
No.

169
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:30,630
My baby is gone.

170
00:15:30,630 --> 00:15:34,780
As the old saying goes, a child that has a destined bone with its parents

171
00:15:34,780 --> 00:15:37,760
