219
00:19:32,100 --> 00:19:36,030
Fourth Lady has not been in a good mood these days. She locked herself in the room.

220
00:19:36,030 --> 00:19:39,560
I was with her in the room.

221
00:19:39,560 --> 00:19:42,360
