232
00:20:16,440 --> 00:20:18,290
Lift her up.

233
00:20:18,290 --> 00:20:20,180
Come.

234
00:20:20,180 --> 00:20:22,310
Next one.

235
00:20:22,310 --> 00:20:25,680
